    {
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {},
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "### Operator Flow\n- Filter to a worker first.\n- Start with **Last Verification**, **Verification Age**, **Current Sync Age**, and the restart counters.\n- If the worker is bad, jump to **Selected Worker** or **Prompt Bundle** in the dashboard links.\n- State timelines answer when the worker changed state. Trend panels answer whether it was lagging, recycling, or simply paused.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Runbook",
      "type": "text"
    },
